n/river flows in you  毒撚如千本櫻 <br />\n一律都係咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋D chord玩到好熟囉 咩key咩chord都可以馬上彈到出黎 就算係D好少見既chord(例如什麼Aaug/Cdim7)都理論上無乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}